text: @FedExHelp Really frustrated with @FedEx right now. 15 calls, infuriating lack of assistance. Tracking number not coming up in system. FedEx saying no lost package case can be opened. Handed the parcel to the driver over 2 weeks ago. Do I just let an expensive box go missing???

@FedExHelp @fedex. Another package missing. This is the third time!  Just called the recipient and there is proof of delivery to the correct address but the person who signed does not work at the company. Please advise asap. Tracking: 782856866628

@wearawishbone @wearawishbone: Have you checked at the front desk with a name similar to J. Lynch? It is extremely important that our drivers do get a signature since that is what the sender requested. Send also your phone # and verify your address please! Sonia
@FedExHelp Hi Sonia. I am having the delivery address check that. My number is 3476016886. Awaiting an update from the delivery address. Will update once I know.
